{
  "stem": "311.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I look at his-- I wanted the end of it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I figured out I-- I was figuring, maybe, I can take somebody with me, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I I was down, very much down.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't know what's going to happen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Matter of fact, when they were taken to Mauthausen-- this was just before when we went to Schindler-- We were four guys hidden, not far from a-- under a German barrack.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We figure, hey, under our barracks, they're going to look.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I mean, this was a German barrack, what they called the [NON-ENGLISH] magazine, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had all the loot stored over there, all the clothes where there would still-- start to give it to us, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were still ripping apart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe, they found a piece of gold here and it was a few dollars or English pounds or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were hidden under there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But-- and then they sent out everybody.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We-- there was only like 300-- no.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "From 40,000, there was left maybe 1,500 people-- From 40,000 Jews?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was more Polacks already than Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the Pole-- the Polish camp was inside our camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had it worse, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- you know, we-- we were all around them, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was still a Polish camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, you know, well, I got kind of hungry.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, we didn't have food to store.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is no food to store, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- I remember, I went to the latrine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I start looking around.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all I see is the Polish uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't see any Jews, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I said, well, what happened, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "What's going to be?",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
